quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"Mbele arii e aade tumo e yonta nde o wonaana hay hu'unde jaŋtateende."
  76,2,"Min tagii aade e toɓɓere jillunde ndiyam gorko e debbo min kumpitoo mbo min laatini mbo nanoowo ji'oowo."
  76,3,"Miin peewnii mbo e laawol o yetta wollo o yedda."
  76,4,"Pellet Miin keblinii he'eferɓe callalle e tonngi e yiite."
  76,5,"Pellet ɗigguɓe ɓe na njara e kaas jilluɗo kaafuur."
  76,6,"Sewnde nde jiyaaɓe Alla ɓallinaaɓe njarata heɓe ilnande ilnugol."
  76,7,"Heɓe kuuɓna takkere hoɓe kula ñalawma mbo bone mum na saroo."
  76,8,"Hoɓe ñammina ñamri wond'ude e yiɗde ndi miskiin e alyatiime e dahaaɗo."
  76,9,"Miin ñamminirta mon ko sabi Alla miin faalaaka e mon njoɓdi wona yetteede."
  76,10,"Pellet min kuli ummaade e joomi amen ko ñalawma ñirɓiniiɗo cattuɗo tumminaare."
  76,11,"Alla reeniɓe e bone oon ñalawma o okkiɓe pummam labaɗam e weltaare."
  76,12,"Alla yoɓiri ɓe koɓe muñi ko aljanna e (comci)hariir."
  76,13,"Hoɓe tuugnii e fotooyji ɓe yi'atah heen na'ange wonah jaangol cattungol."
  76,14,"Na ɓadi e dow mu'en ɗowdi mammba ɓesnaaɗe mum na eeltanaaɓe eeltegol."
  76,15,"Ina taarneeɓe ngennduwoñ kaalis e kaasyoñ na feewnira weer."
  76,16,"Ka'aseeje kaalis hoɗe potndira potndegol."
  76,17,"Hoɓe njarnee kaas njilludi mum ko janjabiil."
  76,18,"Sewnde na e hembo na innire Sal sabiil."
  76,19,"Sukaaɓe saasnaaɓe na mbanngo e mum en si a yi'iiɓe cikka ko ɓe lu'u lu'u caraaɗo."
  76,20,"Si a yi'i toon nji'a neema e laamu manngu."
  76,21,"Ina e dow mu'en comci sundus ɗi mbaadi ha'aka hecco e istabraq ɓe ɓoorna jawe kaalis joom mu'en yarnaɓe njaram laaɓɗam."
  76,22,"Pellet ɗum wonanii mon njoɓdi golle mon kadi golle mon ngoniina mantaaɗe."
  76,23,"Ko minen tigi tellini alquraana e dow ma tellingol."
  76,24,"Muñ e ñaawoore joom ma woto ɗofto e mum en bakkadinɗo wolla ke'efeera."
  76,25,"jaŋta inne joom ma subaka e kikiiɗa."
  76,26,"E jemma he cujjan mbo cubahinanɗaa mbo jehma juutɗo."
  76,27,"Pellet ɓe na njiɗi nguurndam aduna njaawɗam gasde ɗam ɓe ngacca caggal mum en ñalawma nisɗo."
  76,28,"Ko minen tagi on min cemmbini terɗo si min kaajaama min ngostoroo on nandadiiɓe mon gostogol."
  76,29,"Ko nde woni waajo goongo kala paalaaɗo daɗde nanngira fa'ade e joomiiko ruttorde."
  76,30,"On paaletaake si wonaAlla haaje pellet Alla ko ganndo ko ñeeño"
  76,31,"Homo naatna mbo o welaa e yurmeene makko o heblanii tooñɓe ɓe lepte mu'usɗe."
